text:
Food are very YUMMY!
Strongly recommend sour and spicy soup , it’s superb. Tomato soup is nice as well. All with very big portion. Very worth the price
Must add on fried egg, well match with the soups!

Very authentic China local flavour here!

There usually won't be a crowd there so seats are usually available, and it is easier to find parking here.

Soup-wise, quite a lot of flavour to choose from, from non-spicy type to hellish spicy.

Recommend to order deep fried egg together, it tastes so good when soaked into the soup.

The broth was rich and flavorful, and the ingredients were fresh and plentiful. I especially loved the藤椒米线—it had the perfect level of spice! The service was fast and friendly. Definitely coming back!

Delicious and tasty rice noodles in Eco Botanic, must try! A rare hidden gem for Chinese rice noodles as the noodles are delicious, the soup is flavourful and even can get unlimited noodle refills-truly amazingly. Will definitely be coming back.
Second time visit. Love their Guizhou sour soup so much!! Full of mixian and ingredients for only RM16.8. Definitely will come back again for this .
